jms -java message service
---------------------------
Java Message Service is an API which supports the formal communication called as messaging between computers on a network.
It provides a common interface for standard message protocols and message services in support to the Java programs.
It provides facility to create, send and read messages. 
The JMS API reduces the concepts that a programmer must learn to use the messaging services/products and it also provides the features that support the messaging applications

benefits of jms
----------------
asynchronous-to recevie a message it need not requried to send the request ,message arrrives automatcally.
reliable-meeage is delivered only once .jms hepls to avoid ploblems that duplicate messages createproblems.

